coff price bad news for latin america -minist a senior nicaraguan offici said a recent plung in coff price wa econom and polit disastr for latin american coffee-produc countri . nicaraguan foreign trade minist alejandro martinez cuenca wa in london to brief intern coff organi ( ico ) execut board produc member after a meet last weekend in managua attend by eight latin american coff produc to discuss the fall in coff price . london coff price slid 300 stg per tonn in march , to 1,279 stg from 1,580 stg at end-februari . martinez told report the price fall sinc the ico fail to agr export quota on march 1 ha had disastr result on latin america , both econom and polit . he urg continu negoti among coff produc to pave the way for a coff export quota agreement by septemb . coff export quota , use to regul coff price under an intern coff agreement , were suspend a year ago when price soar in respon to a drought in brazil . central american econom minist have estim the region will lose 720 mln dlr in foreign exchang earn in 1987 if coff price are not rescu by a quota arrang , martinez said . he said ico quota talk broke down last month becau consum member lack the polit will to fulli support commod agreement , and becau consum tri to dictat to produc .